{
  "stem": "22685.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when he told that it was a total destruction of all the people, not only from Lutsk, but all the Jews from the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] villages and towns around Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because Lutsk was the major town in this state.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In Lublin, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I met people from my town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I met some friends, people from Numir who knew my family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after maybe a month later came Fenia's husband, who grew up on the same street where I grew up.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we knew each other all our lives.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He wanted-- was sent to the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And for him-- for me, I didn't have a legal dismissal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But for him, I knew the, the, the editor of the paper, of the communist paper, was a man from Lutsk, [NON-ENGLISH], that I knew from before the war.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when he, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] he gave us a contact to get-- to be free from the army legally.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We stayed in Lublin a couple of months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I was arrested.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I ran away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But that's a different story, so it'll-- two little adventures.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we made fake papers that we are going to [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Hungary.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we traveled.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "While we were on the train, the war ended in May of-- May or June of '45.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We were in the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know how much detail you want to hear because there were so many things happening in the-- times were not normal.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we behaved also not in a normal-- not in a completely rational way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because if we would be rational, we wouldn't take those chances.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Anyhow, we left Russia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We came to Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We go now to Romania.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
